enc_source_echo_filename(25.10)                enc_source_echo_filename(25.10)

Name
       enc_source_echo_filename

Syntax
        enc_source_echo_filename <value>

       Type: Boolean

       Default: 0

       When  this  setting is enabled, the log file will display the file name
       being sourced before the actually sourcing the file. By  default,  name
       of the file being sourced is not displayed in the log file.

